Description: Nion Swift EELS Analysis
        ========================
        
        A Nion Swift library for EELS analysis (used in Nion Swift)
        -----------------------------------------------------------
        Nion Swift EELS analysis is comprised of libraries and UI's useful for EELS
        analysis.
        
